Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.57,0:00:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,银河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.05,0:00:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危机，这下糟糕了\N紧张！紧张！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.65,0:00:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扑克光线BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡闹一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.69,0:00:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没关系，吃个饮茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.46,0:00:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着欢悦的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.66,0:00:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后一起向神明祈祷吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.07,0:00:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.44,0:00:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.21,0:00:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就让它顺其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.75,0:00:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有机关，没有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.22,0:00:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一掷的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.35,0:01:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无忧无虑的狂欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.96,0:01:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦想与希望的机关枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.79,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,锁定想要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧，BRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.77,0:01:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人兴奋的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.60,0:01:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开辟天下无敌的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(佛特的遗迹炖煮麻烦酱菜)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.99,0:01:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种地方会有遗迹吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就是为了\N调查这个而来的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得好恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.60,0:01:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，这里好像坟场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.14,0:01:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个在怕什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.24,0:01:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里什么也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,几千年前这个星球早已灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.75,0:02:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算有生物的话\N也只有我们而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.69,0:02:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...那再挖下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.52,0:02:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该不会\N有鬼之类的东西出现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冤枉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.96,0:02:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要吓我啦！佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.97,0:02:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木乃伊也好，吸血鬼也好\N都出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会比这无聊的挖掘工作\N还要有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些人真是够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说了什么呀？诺麦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说的没错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们现在正站在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.58,0:02:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,记录了数千年历史的\N伟大遗迹前耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样虔敬的心情或是浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们一点都没有感觉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.66,0:02:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法式糖炒栗子的话\N我蛮会做的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.77,0:02:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然和这种无知、无教养\N无神经的人一起出来是错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.94,0:02:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是香草的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.81,0:03:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会同意我的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，若能跟香草一起来该有多好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什么？佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很危险耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这么讨厌我们的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.95,0:03:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干脆把你绑在飞弹上\N送回香草所在的基地好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用麻烦了，谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.56,0:03:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那以后你说话要注意一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦，我们快点完成任务吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像又找到什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.84,0:03:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然，你的好运异于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.45,0:03:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是\N好像跟遗迹没多大关系耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是蛋耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？怎么敲不破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想吃掉它吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是想要吃掉它吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.24,0:04:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是变成化石了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老鼠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特你看，好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.60,0:04:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪...哪里可爱了啊？这种小老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.84,0:04:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，这家伙在瞪我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊，佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是刚刚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.88,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是你搞错了\N对不对？小可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.52,0:04:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，它这么可爱\N怎么会瞪人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.05,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还很黏人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要不要抱抱看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:05:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要...今天不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不必客气啊，来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是跟你说过我不要的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特你怎么了？流好多汗耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.08,0:05:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么可以这样子，佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.59,0:05:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.36,0:05:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特你原来...真令人意外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人真的是不可貌相啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.74,0:05:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连哭泣的小孩\N看到都会安静的佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然也有害怕的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.98,0:05:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且怕的还是小老鼠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.78,0:05:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.82,0:05:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特你怕它吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么可爱耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把这小老鼠丢掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.83,0:06:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮它取名叫  “小太”  吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样，喜欢吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还呵呵咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.24,0:06:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把它丢掉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.44,0:06:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特你去把它丢掉不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样一来事情就简单多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛...还是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫非你不敢摸老鼠吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.72,0:06:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀！这件事\N要是让天使队的人知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会吓一跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.86,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该说，大家一定笑破肚皮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.66,0:06:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去有笑话可以跟大家说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德，你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是你希望我，不要告诉大家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这是和我谈条件吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.97,0:06:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你答应我不伤害小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不会跟大家说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.78,0:07:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有\N以后你不能再称呼我"这家伙"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了\N太好了，小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.42,0:07:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了！我抓到佛特的弱点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来可以过一阵好日子了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.14,0:07:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特\N要不要过来这边吃饭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有热汤可喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了，我没食欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真稀奇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特竟然也会没食欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.36,0:07:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...要继续去找遗迹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过敏虽然是退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，我竟被那两个人瞧不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.81,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都是那只臭老鼠的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，好痒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫非...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙也在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要在那边鬼鬼崇崇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.06,0:08:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要亲手杀了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出来吧！小老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然敢耍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就让你见识见识\N我真的生气时是什么样子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你不是普通的老鼠吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.36,0:08:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太，小太你在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.47,0:09:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，小太你在这里呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特有没有欺负你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离这家伙远一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要叫它"这家伙"了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的名字叫作"小太"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么小太呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你给我听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙，嘴巴会吐出光线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一瞬间就把这火箭炮\N开了个洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.36,0:09:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙是披了老鼠皮的怪物呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会是怪物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.37,0:09:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是佛特说这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.57,0:09:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才害小太吓跑了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙怎么可能被吓跑嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太它...小太它...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变这么大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.79,0:10:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么可爱的小太竟然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正所谓小时了了\N大未必佳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是这个问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.41,0:10:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是破坏幕斯卡文明的生物武器\NBIOTECH  WEAPON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太是武器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么可以\N把这么重要的事给忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健忘症嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人都会有的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健忘症？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙还算是电脑吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.03,0:10:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙果然是怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可怕的瘟神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.83,0:10:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论它变得多大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太还是小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是笨蛋吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它可是生物武器呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.92,0:10:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.98,0:10:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它在太空中也能生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许会去其他星球\N闹得天翻地覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑\N这是真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.16,0:11:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你把蛋弄破的\N你要想办法解决喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，怎么这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.14,0:11:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想到一个好方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.18,0:11:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就叫作废物利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你利用了老鼠的本能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.79,0:11:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管它的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.82,0:11:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概会转一辈子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太看起来好开心的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(下个菜单是\N游乐园名产，鸡肉薄荷蜜饯)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.17,0:11:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花．法兰波瓦兹\N与佛特．修特伦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.80,0:11:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两人在那天冲进了枪林弹雨中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.34,0:11:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两人就再也没有回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,满天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.64,0:12:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我新月的曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.48,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做了梦之后，变得想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侧耳倾听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.75,0:12:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是听见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.29,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人兴奋的天线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.27,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要让它睡着  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,处女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.38,0:13:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向巨蟹座的你发出\N急电，急电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.41,0:13:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘着飞马的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.72,0:13:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DARLING  LOVING  YOU

